      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical benchmark suite (MAPDL verification manual problems VM6, VM25, VM67) was executed under both the rc2 and production build-7 executables. Results were numerically identical to five significant figures, supporting the analyst's assertion that no material solver change occurred between builds. Gradation 2 is achieved."
